			Contact Us
		

                                









​Altria Group is the parent company of Philip Morris USA, U.S. Smokeless Tobacco Company, John Middleton, Ste. Michelle Wine Estates, Nu Mark and Philip Morris Capital Corporation .
Tobacco Product Questions 
If you have a product question or concern for one of Altria's tobacco operating companies, please contact them here: 













Philip Morris USA​800-627-5200Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-7 p.m. (ET)U.S. Smokeless Tobacco Company800-650-7411Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-7 p.m. (ET) John Middleton888-878-4562Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-7 p.m. (ET) Nu Mark855-627-5836Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-7 p.m. (ET) 




















For Information OnPM USA's products, such as Marlboro? Learn More
USSTC's smokeless products, such as Copenhagen and Skoal? Learn More 
Middleton's cigars, such as Black & Mild? Learn More  Stand up - Speak Out​​​Help fight unfair tax increases


 


For information on current legislative and regulatory issues, visit:


 


​ 


Citizens for Tobacco Rights​


 


Informing & Engaging Adult Tobacco Consumers


 


YOU CAN MAKE A DIFFERENCE
​ Law Enforcement​​​If you are a member of law enforcement in need of support related to illicit trade in tobacco please call the Law Enforcement Support Line at 877-224-3487. Still Have a Question?​​If you still have a question, email us​ 

















General FAQsInvestor FAQsProduct FAQsFAQsGeneral FAQsInvestor FAQsProduct FAQs​How can I obtain information about or report a quality issue with a tobacco product manufactured by one of your tobacco operating companies?​Please refer to the list of Altria's tobacco operating companies at the top of this page. The list includes the name of the company, toll-free number and hours of operation.
If you are calling about a specific product you purchased, you can also call the toll-free number on the packageProduct FAQs​​​How can I obtain information about a promotion for a tobacco product manufactured by one of your tobacco operating companies?​You may contact the Customer Service Department of Altria's tobacco operating companies using the numbers below. Callers must be eligible tobacco consumers 21 years of age or older.
For more information about the marketing practices of Altria's tobacco operating companies, please refer to the Marketing Practices section on our website.

Philip Morris USA800-627-5200Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-10 p.m. (ET)Saturday-Sunday, 9 a.m.-5 p.m. (ET)

U.S. Smokeless Tobacco800-650-7411Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-10 p.m. (ET)Saturday, 9 a.m.-5 p.m. (ET)

John Middleton Company888-878-4562Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-10 p.m. (ET)Saturday-Sunday, 9 a.m.-5 p.m. (ET)
​
Nu Mark855-627-5836Monday-Friday, 9 a.m.-7 p.m. (ET)
​
Or you can email us.
