Our Approach
          

Working to develop and market tobacco products that could be less harmful and talking with the FDA about them.
    


     

Providing a wider variety of tobacco products for adult consumers as their preferences
        evolve.
    


     

Taking a responsible approach that will allow us to continue to be the leader in
        the tobacco industry.
    
 

         
    

        Our Focus​
    
          ​


More than 8,000 employees coast to coast
Hundreds of thousands of retailers in all 50 states
U.S. farmers who work in the fields
Adult consumers who choose our products
Communities where we live and work.  In 2016,
            
​We donated $55.9 million in cash and in-kind contributions nationally.
Our employees contributed 45,000 hours of community service through volunteer activities.
95% of our executives served on non­-profit boards.​





 
    
